    "body": "Hi @e-krebs \r\nwe don't guarantee we reuse the DOM across renders (destroying or reusing DOM is decided by our component abstraction Preact).\r\n\r\nHere when you click on a DOM element, we mutate the DOM and sometimes destroy the checkbox instead of reusing it. \r\nIf you want to hook some specific behaviour to the component after a refine call, I would advise creating your own component on top of the connector, so that you have full control on the DOM.\r\n\r\nI hope this helps. Closing for now but feel free to reopen if i missed something.\r\n ",
